I'll up my position in bdc CODI a little now.

CODI is different from most other bdc's of course in that it takes controlling
interest in the companies in which it makes investments. Which gives them
another way to make money other than by lending it to the companies. That is,
they can control if/when the companies themselves are sold. Which they seem to
be doing successfully.

